hadiths[82]{hadithnumber,text}:
521,"Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne aik din (asr ki) Namaz mein der ki, to Urwa-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif le gaey, aur unhon-ne bataya ke (usi tarah) Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik din ( Iraq ke mulk mein) Namaz mein der ki thi jab wo Iraq main ( Hakim ( they. to Abu-Masood Ansari ( Aqba bin umr ( unki khidmat mein gaey aur farmaya, Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ! aakhir ye kya baat hai, kya aapko malum nahi ke jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) tashrif laey to unhon-ne Namaz padhi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi Namaz padhi, phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne Namaz padhi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi Namaz padhi, phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne Namaz padhi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi Namaz padhi, phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke main isi tarah hukm diya gaya hun. is par Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne Urwa se kaha, malum bhi hai aap kya bayan kar rahe hain? kya Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ke oqaat (amal karke ) bataaey they. Urwa ne kaha, ke yahan isi tarah Basheer-bin-abii- Masood (Raziallahu anhu) apne walid ke waaste se bayan kartey they."
522,Urwa (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke mujh se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz us waqt padh letey they jab abhi dhoop unke hujre mein maujood hoti thi us se bhi pahley ke wo diwar par chadhey.
523,"abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha ke ham us Rabee qabeele se hain aur ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein sirf hurmat waley mahinon hi mein hazir ho saktey hain, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi aisi baat ka hamein hukm dijiye, jisey ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se seekh lein aur apne peechhey rehney waley doosrey logon ko bhi uski dawat de sakein , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen char chizon ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa hon, pahley Allah par eman laney ka, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski tafseel bayan farmai ke is baat ki shahadat dena ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke main Allah ka rasool hun, aur doosrey Namaz qaaim karne ka, teesrey zakat dene ka, aur chauthey jo maal tumhen ghaneemat mein miley, usmein se panchwan hissey ada karne ka aur tumhen mein tonbdi hantam, qasaar aur naqeer ke istemal se roktaa hun. (note : ye tamam bartan sharab banaaney ke liye istemal hotey they)."
524,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daste-mubaarak par Namaz qaaim karne, zakat diye, aur har musalman ke sath khair khahi karne par bait ki."
525,"ham umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they ke aap ne puchha ke fitne se mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki koi hadis tum mein se kisi ko yad hai? mein bola, maine usey (usi tarah yad rakha hai) jaisey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us hadis ko bayan farmaya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) boley, ke tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se fitan ko malum karne mein bahut be-baak they. maine kaha ke insan ke ghar waale, maal aulad aur padosi sab fitna (ki cheez ( hain. aur namaaz, roza, sadqa , achi baat ke liye logon ko hukm karna aur buri baton se roknaa un fitnon ka kaffara hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke main tum se iske mutaalliq nahi poochhta , mujhey tum us fitne ke barey mein batlao jo samandar ki mauj ki tarah thaathein maarta hua badhega. is par maine kaha ke ya ameerul-momineen! aap us se khof na khaaiye. aap ke aur fitne ke darmyan aik band darwaza hai. puchha kya wo darwaza tod diya jaeyga ya ( sirf ( khola jaeyga maine kaha ke tod diya jaeyga umr (Raziallahu anhu) bol uthey, ke phir to wo kabhi band nahi ho sakega. Shaqiq ne kaha ke ham ne Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya umr (Raziallahu anhu) us darwaze ke mutaalliq kuchh ilm rakhtey they, to unhon-ne kaha ke yahan! bilkul isi tarah jaisey din ke baad raat ke aaney kaa. maine tum se aik aisi hadis bayan ki hai jo qat'an ghalat nahi hai. hamein iske mutaalliq Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se poochhney mein dar hota tha (ke darwaze se kya murad hai) isliye ham ne Masruq se kaha (ke wo poochhein ( unhon-ne malum kya to aap ne bataya ke wo darwaza khud umr (Raziallahu anhu) hi they."
526,"aik shakhs ne kisi ghair aurat ka bosa ley liya aur phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur aapko us harkat ki khabar de di. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai, ke Namaz din ke donon hisson mein qaaim karo aur kuchh raat gaey bhi, aur bila shubah nekiyan buraaiyon ko mitaa deti hain. us shakhs ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! kya ye sirf mere liye hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke meri tamam ummat ke liye yahi hukm hai."
527,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke Allah Taala ki bargah mein kon sa amal zyada mahboob hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne waqt par Namaz padhnaa, phir poochha, iske ba'd? farmaya waalidain ke sath nek mamla rakhna. puchha iske ba'd, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki raah mein jihad karna. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ye tafseel batai aur agar main aur sawalat karta to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur zyada bhi batlatey .) lekin maine bataur adab khamoshi ikhtiyar ki) ."
528,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke agar kisi shakhs ke darwazey par nehar jari ho aur wo rozaana usmein panch paanch baar nahaaey to tumhara kya guman hai. kya uske badan par kuchh bhi mail baqi reh sakta hai? sahaba ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! hargiz nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahi haal panchon waqt ki namazon ka hai ke Allah paak unke zariey se gunahon ko mitaa deta hai.
529,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad ki koi baat us zamane mein nahi paata. logon ne kaha, Namaz to hai. farmaya iske andar bhi tum ne kar rakha hai jo kar rakha hai."
530,main dimashq mein Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein gaya. aap us waqt ro rahe they. maine arz kya ke aap kyon ro rahe hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur ki koi cheez is Namaz ke ilawa ab main nahi paata aur ab usko bhi zaaye kar diya gaya hai. aur Bakr-bin-Khalaf ne kaha ke ham se Muhammad-bin-Bakar barsani ne bayan kya ke ham se Usmaan-bin-abii-Rawaad ne yahi hadis bayan ki.
531,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein hota hai to wo apne rab se sargoshi karta rehta hai isliye apni dahini taraf na thookna chahiye lekin baaein paon ke nichey thook sakta hai.
532,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sajda karne mein aetidaal rakho (seedhii tarah par karo) aur koi shakhs tum mein se apne baazuon ko kuttey ki tarah na phailaaey. jab kisi ko thookna hi ho to samney ya dahini taraf na thookey, kyonke wo Namaz main apne rab se posheeda baatein karta rehta hai aur Saeed ne Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat karke bayan kya hai ke aagey ya samney na thookey albatta baain taraf paon ke nichey thook sakta hai aur Shoba ne kaha ke apne samney aur daain taraf na thookey, balke baain taraf ya paon ke nichey thook sakta hai. aur Humaid ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke qible ki taraf na thookey aur na daain taraf albatta baain taraf ya paon ke nichey thook sakta hai."
533,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab garmi tez ho jaey to Namaz ko thandey waqt mein padho, kyonke garmi ki tezi jahannam ki aag ki bhap se hoti hai."
534,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab garmi tez ho jaey to Namaz ko thandey waqt mein padho, kyonke garmi ki tezi jahannam ki aag ki bhap se hoti hai."
535,"ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke muazzan ( Bilal ( ne Zohar ki azan di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thanda kar, thanda kar, ya ye farmaya ke intizar kar, intizar kar, aur farmaya ke garmi ki tezi jahannam ki aag ki bhap se hai. isliye jab garmi sakht ho jaey to Namaz thandey waqt mein padha karo, phir Zohar ki azan us waqt kahi gaee jab ham ne teelon ke saaey dekh liye."
536,"jab garmi tez ho jaey to Namaz ko thandey waqt mein padha karo, kyonke garmi ki tezi dozakh ki aag ki bhap ki wjah se hoti hai."
537,"dozakh ne apne rab se shikayat ki ke aey mere rab! ( aag ki shiddat ki wjah se) mere kuchh hisse ne kuchh hisse ko kha liya hai is par Allah Taala ne usey 2 saans leney ki ijazat di, aik saans jaadey main aur aik saans garmi mein. ab intihai sakht garmi aur sakht sardi jo tum log mehsus kartey ho wo usi se paida hoti hai."
538,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (ke garmi ke mausam mein) Zohar ko thandey waqt mein padha karo, kyonke garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki bhap se paida hoti hai. is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) Sufiyan sory, Yahya aur abu-Awana ne Aamash ke waaste se ki hai."
539,"ham aik safar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. muazzan ne chaha ke Zohar ki azan de. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke waqt ko thanda honey do, muazzan ne (thodi der baad) phir chaha ke azan de, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thanda honey do. jab hamne teeley ka saaya dhala hua dekh liya. (tab azan kahi gai) phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke garmi ki tezi jahannam ki bhap ki tezi se hai. isliye jab garmi sakht ho jaya karey to Zohar ki Namaz thandey waqt mein padha karo. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ( يتفيئو ( (ka lafz jo sura النحل mein hai) ke matlab ( تتميل‏ ( ( jhukna , maail hona) hain."
540,"jab suraj dhala to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hujre se bahar tashrif laey aur Zohar ki Namaz padhi. phir member par tashrif laey aur qiyamat ka zikr farmaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat mein badey azeem mamley pesh aaeingey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar kisi ko kuchh poochhna ho to poochh ley. kyonke jab tak main is jagah par hun tum mujh se jo bhi poochhogey, main uska jawab zaroor doonga. log bahut zyada roney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barabar farmatey jatey they ke jo kuchh poochhna ho poochho. Abdullaah-bin-Huzaafa Sehmi khadey huey aur malum kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere bap kon hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey bap Huzafa they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ab bhi barabar farma rahe they ke poochho kya poochhtey ho. itney mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) adab se ghutnon ke bal baith gaey aur unhon-ne farmaya ke ham Allah Taala ke Malik honey, Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Nabi honey se razi aur khush hain. ( to is gustakhi se ham baaz aatey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja aur be-jaa sawalat karein) is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke abhi-abhi mere samney jannat aur jahannam us diwar ke koney mein pesh ki gaee thi. to maine na aisi koi umda cheez dekhi (jaisi jannat thi) aur na koi aisi buri cheez dekhi (jaisi dozakh thi)."
541,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz us waqt padhtey they jab ham apne paas baithey huey shakhs ko pehchan letey they. subah ki Namaz main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 60 se 100 tak aayatein padhtey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar us waqt padhtey jab suraj dhal jata aur Asr ki Namaz us waqt ke ham Madina Munawra ki aakhiri had tak (namaz padhney ke baad) jatey lekin suraj ab bhi tez rehta tha. namaaze-maghrib ka Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo waqt bataya tha wo mujhey yad nahi raha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isha ki Namaz ko tehai raat tak der karne mein koi haraj nahi samajhtey they, phir Abul-Minhaal ne kaha ke aadhi raat tak (deri karne mein) koi haraj nahi samajhtey they. aur Muaz ne kaha ke Shoba ne farmaya ke phir main dobara Abul-Minhaal se mila to unhon-ne farmaya '' ya tehai raat tak '' ."
542,"jab ham ( garmiyon mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Zohar ki Namaz do-pahar din mein padhtey they, to garmi se bachney ke liye kapdon par sajda kya kartey."
543,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina mein reh kar 7 rakaat (eik saath) aur 8 rakaat (eik saath) padhin. Zohar aur Asr (ki 8 rakaat (aur maghrib aur isha (ki 7 rakaat ( Ayub sakhtiyan ne Jaabir bin Zaid se puchha shayad barsat ka mausam raha ho. Jaabir bin Zaid ne jawab diya ke ghaaliban aisa hi hoga.
544,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz aisey waqt padhtey they ke unke hujre mein se abhi dhoop bahar nahi nikalti thi.
545,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ki Namaz padhi to dhoop unke hujre hi mein thi. saaya wahan nahi phaila tha.
546,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Asr ki Namaz padhtey to suraj abhi mere hujrey mein jhankta rehta tha. abhi saya na phaila hota tha. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( kehtey hain ke Imam Malik aur Yahya bin Saeed, Shuaib (Rahmatullahi-alaih) aur ibne-abi Hafsa ke riwayaton mein (Zohri se) (والشمس قبل أن تظهر) ke alfaz hain, (jinka matlab ye hai ke dhoop abhi uper na chadhi hoti ( ."
547,main aur mere bap abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. unse mere walid ne puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farz namazein kin waqton mein padhtey they. unhon-ne farmaya ke do-pahar ki Namaz jisey tum '' pehli Namaz '' kehtey ho suraj dhalney ke baad padhtey they. aur jab Asr padhtey iske baad koi shakhs Madina ke intihai kinare par apne ghar wapas jata to suraj ab bhi tez hota tha. Sayyar ne kaha ke maghrib ke waqt ke mutaalliq aap ne jo kuchh kaha tha wo mujhey yad nahi raha aur isha ki Namaz jisey tum ( عتمه ( kehtey ho usmein der ko pasand farmatey they aur us se pahley soney ko aur uske baad baat cheet karne ko na-pasand farmatey aur subah ki Namaz se us waqt farigh ho jatey jab aadmi apne qareeb baithey huey doosrey shakhs ko pehchan sakta aur subah ki Namaz mein aap 60-100 tak aayatein padha kartey they.
548,ham Asr ki Namaz padh chuktey aur uske baad koi bani Amr-bin-Auf ( Quba ( ki masjid mein jata to unko wahan Asr ki Namaz padhtey huey paata.
549,ham ne Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke sath Zohar ki Namaz padhi. phir ham nikal kar Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to dekha aap Namaz padh rahe hain. maine kaha ke aey mukarram chacha ! ye kon si Namaz aap ne padhi hai. farmaya ke Asr ki aur usi waqt ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bhi ye Namaz padhtey they.
550,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Asr ki Namaz padhtey to suraj buland aur tez roshan hota tha. phir aik shakhs Madina ke oopri ilaqe ki taraf jata wahan pahunchne ke baad bhi suraj buland rehta tha (Zohri ne kaha ke) Madina ke oopri ilaqe ke kuchh maqamat taqriban char mail par ya kuchh aisey hi waaqe hain.
551,ham Asr ki Namaz padhtey (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saath) iske baad koi shakhs Quba jata aur jab wahan pahunch jata to suraj abhi buland hota tha.
552,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jiski namaze-Asr chhoot gaee maano iska ghar aur maal sab lut gaya. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne farmaya ke sura Muhammad mein jo ( يترکم (ka lafz aaya hai wo ( witr ( se nikala gaya hai. ( witr ( kehtey hain kisi shakhs ka koi aadmi mar daalnaa ya uska maal chheen lenaa."
553,"ham Barida (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath aik safar jang mein they. abr w barish ka din tha. aap ne farmaya ke Asr ki Namaz jaldi padh lo. kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Asr ki Namaz chhod di, iska nek amal zaaye ho gaya."
554,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chaand par aik nazar dali phir farmaya ke tum apne rab ko) aakhirat mein) isi tarah dekhogey jaisey us chaand ko ab dekh rahe ho. iske dekhney main tum ko koi zahmat bhi nahi hogi, to agar tum aisa kar saktey ho ke suraj tuloo honey se pahley wali Namaz ( fajr (aur suraj ghurub honey se pahley wali Namaz (asr ( se tumhen koi cheez rok na sakey to aisa zaroor karo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmai ke ''pas apne Malik ki hamd w tasbeeh kar suraj tuloo honey aur ghurub honey se pahley.'' Ismail (hadees ke raawii) ne kaha ke (asr aur fajr ki namaazein) tum se chhootney na paaein. unka hamesha khas taur par dhyaan rakho."
555,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raat aur din mein farishton ki dutiyaan badaltii rehti hain. aur fajr aur Asr ki namazon main ( duty par aaney walon aur rukhsat paaney walon ka ( ijtimaa hota hai. phir tumharey paas rehney waley Farishtey jab uper chadhtey hain to Allah Taala poochhta hai halanke wo unse bahut zyada apne bandon ke mutaalliq janta hai, ke mere bandon ko tum ne kis haal mein chhoda . wo jawab detey hain ke ham ne jab unhein chhoda to wo ( fajr ki) Namaz padh rahe they aur jab unke paas gaey tab bhi wo (asr ki) Namaz padh rahe they."
556,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar Asr ki Namaz ki aik rakaat bhi koi shakhs suraj ghurub honey se pahley pa saka to poori Namaz padhey (iski Namaz ada hui na qazaa) isi tarah agar suraj tuloo honey se pahley fajr ki Namaz ki aik rakaat bhi pa sakey to poori Namaz padhey.
557,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke tum se pahley ki ummaton ke muqaabla mein tumhari zindagi sirf itni hai jitna Asr se suraj doobney tak ka waqt hota hai. Taurah walon ko Taurah di gaee. to unhon-ne is par) subah se) amal kya. aadhey din tak phir wo aajiz aa gaey, kaam pura na kar sakey, un logon ko unke amal ka badla eik-eik qirat diya gaya. phir Injeel walon ko Injeel di gaee, unhon-ne (aadhey din se) Asr tak is par amal kya, aur wo bhi aajiz aa gaey. unko bhi eik-eik qirat unke amal ka badla diya gaya. phir (asr ke waqt) ham ko Quran mila. ham ne is par suraj ke ghurub honey tak amal kya (aur kaam pura kar diyaa) hamein 2-2 qirat sawab mila. is par un donon kitab walon ne kaha, aey hamarey parwardigaar! unhein to aap ne 2-2 qirat diye aur hamein sirf eik-eik qeeraat. halanke amal ham ne unse zyada kya. izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya, to kya maine ajr dene main tum par kuchh zulm kya. unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. Allah Taala ne farmaya ke phir ye (zyaada ajr denaa) mera Fazal hai jisey main chaahoon de sakta hun."
558,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalmanon aur yahood w nasara ki misal aik aisey shakhs ki si hai ke jisne kuchh logon se mazdoorii par raat tak kaam karne ke liye kaha, unhon-ne aadhey din kaam kya. phir jawab de diya ke hamein tumhari ujrat ki zarurat nahi, (ye yahood they) phir us shakhs ne doosrey mazdoor bulaey aur unse kaha ke din ka jo hissey baqi bach gaya hai (yani aadha din) usi ko pura kar do. shart ke mutabiq mazdoorii tumhen milegii. unhon-ne bhi kaam shuru kya lekin Asr tak wo bhi jawab de baithey. (ye nasara they) to us teesrey giroh ne (jo ahal Islam hain) pahley 2 girohon ke kaam ki poori mazdoorii ley li."
559,aap ne farmaya ke ham maghrib ki Namaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padh kar jab wapas hotey aur teer andazi kartey (to itna ujaalaa baqi rehta tha ke) aik shakhs apne teer girney ki jagah ko dekhta tha.
560,Hajjaj ka zamana aaya (aur wo Namaz der karke padhaayaa karta tha us liye) ham ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se iske barey mein puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz theek do-pahar mein padhaayaa kartey they. abhi suraj saaf aur roshan hota to namaze-Asr padhaatey. namaze-Maghrib waqt aatey hi padhatey aur Namaz isha ko kabhi jaldi padhatey aur kabhi der se. jab dekhtey ke log jama ho gaey hain to jaldi padha detey aur agar log jaldi jama na hotey to Namaz mein der kartey. (aur logon ka intizar kartey (aur subah ki Namaz sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ya (ye kaha ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andherey mein padhtey they.
561,ham namaze-Maghrib Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us waqt padhtey they jab suraj pardey mein chhup jata.
562,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saat (7) rakaat ( maghrib aur isha ki) aik sath aath (8) rakaat (zuhar aur Asr ki namaazein) aik sath padhin.
563,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aisa na ho ke '' maghrib '' ki Namaz ke naam ke liye Eiraab (yani dehati logon) ka muhaawara tumhari zabanon par chadh jaey. Abdullaah-bin-Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke badwi maghrib ko isha kehtey they."
564,aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein isha ki Namaz padhai. yahi jisey log ( عتمه ( kehtey hain. phir hamein Khattab kartey huey farmaya ke tum us raat ko yad rakhna. aaj jo log zinda hain aik 100 saal ke guzarney tak poori zameen par unmein se koi bhi baqi nahi rahega.
565,"ham ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein malum kya. to aap ne farmaya ke aap namaze-Zohar do-pahar mein padhtey they. aur jab namaze-Asr padhtey to suraj saaf roshan hota. maghrib ki Namaz wajib hotey hi ada farmatey, aur '' isha ''main agar log jaldi jama ho jatey to jaldi padh letey aur agar aaney walon ki tadaad kam hoti to der kartey aur subah ki Namaz munh andherey mein padha kartey they."
566,aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz der se padhi. ye Islam ke phailney se pahley ka waqia hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tak bahar tashrif nahi laey jab tak umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye na farmaya ke auratein aur bachchey so gaey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur farmaya ke tumharey ilawa duniya mein koi bhi insan us Namaz ka intizar nahi karta.
567,"maine apne un sathiyon ke sath jo kashtii mein mere sath ( Habsha se) aaey they ''Baqee' Bat'haan'' mein qiyam kya. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina mein tashrif rakhtey they. ham mein se koi na koi isha ki Namaz mein rozaana baari muqarrar karke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua karta tha. ittifaq se main aur mere aik sathi aik martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne kisi kaam mein mashghool they. (kisi millii maamle mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) guftgu farma rahe they) jiski wjah se Namaz mein der ho gaee aur taqriban aadhi raat guzar gaee. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur Namaz padhai. Namaz poori kar chukey to haaziriin se farmaya ke apni apni jagah par waqaar ke sath baithey raho aur aik khushkhabri suno. tumharey siwa duniya mein koi bhi aisa aadmi nahi jo us waqt Namaz padhta ho, ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke tumharey siwa us waqt kisi ( ummat ( ne bhi Namaz nahi padhi thi. ye yaqin nahi ke aap ne un 2 jumlon mein se kon sa jumla kaha tha. phir rawi ne kaha ke abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, to ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye sun kar bahut hi khush ho kar lautey."
568,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isha se pahley soney aur uske baad baat-cheet karne ko na-pasand farmatey they.
569,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik baar isha ki Namaz mein der farmai. yahan tak ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne pukaaraa, namaaz! auratein aur bachchey sab so gaey. tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar se bahar tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke saari zameen par tumharey ilawa aur koi us Namaz ka intizar nahi karta. rawi ne kaha, us waqt ye Namaz (baa-jamaa't) Madina ke siwa aur kahin nahi padhi jati thi. sahaba us Namaz ko Sham ki surkhi ke ghayab honey ke baad raat ke pahley tehai hisse tak ( kisi waqt bhi) padhtey they."
570,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik raat kisi kaam mein mashghool ho gaey aur bahut der ki. ham (namaz ke intizar mein baithey huey) masjid hi mein so gaey, phir ham bedaar huey, phir ham so gaey, phir ham bedaar huey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar se bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya ke duniya ka koi shakhs bhi tumharey siwa us Namaz ka intizar nahi karta. agar neend ka ghalba na hota to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) isha ko pahley padhney ya baad mein padhney ko koi ahmiyat nahi detey they. kabhi Namaz isha se pahley aap so bhi letey they. ibn-Juraij ne kaha maine Ata se malum kya."
571,"maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik raat isha ki Namaz mein der ki jiske nateeja mein log (masjid hi mein) so gaey. phir bedaar huey phir so gaey, phir bedaar huey. aakhir mein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur pukara '' Namaz '' Ata ne kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar se tashrif laey. wo manzar meri nigahon ke samney hai jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar Mubarak se pani ke qatrey tapak rahe they aur aap hath sar par rakhey huey they. aap ne farmaya ke agar meri ummat ke liye mushkil na ho jaatii, to main unhein hukm deta ke isha ki Namaz ko usi waqt padhein. maine Ata se mazeed tahqeeq chahi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath sar par rakhney ki kaifiyat kya thi? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein is silsiley mein kis tarah khabar di thi. is par Ata ne apne hath ki ungliyan thodi si khol dein aur unhein sar ke aik kinarey par rakha phir unhein mila kar yun sar par pherney lagey ke unka angoothaa kaan ke us kinarey se jo chehrey se qareeb hai aur dadhi se ja laga. na sustii ki aur na jaldii, balke is tarah kya aur kaha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar meri ummat par mushkil na guzarti to main hukm deta ke us Namaz ko usi waqt padha karein."
572,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik din) isha ki Namaz aadhi raat gaey padhi aur farmaya ke doosrey log Namaz padh kar so gaey hongey. (yani dusri masaajid mein padhney waley musalman (aur tum log jab tak Namaz ka intizar kartey rahe ( maano sarey waqt) Namaz hi padhtey rahe. ibne-Maryam ne usmein ye zyada kya ke hamein Yahya bin Ayub ne khabar di. kaha mujh se Humaid lamba ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye suna, maano us raat aap ki anguthi ki chamak ka naqsha us waqt bhi meri nazron ke samney chamak raha hai."
573,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chaand ki taraf nazar uthai jo chaudahwiin raat ka tha. phir farmaya ke tum log be-tok apne rab ko isi tarah dekhogey jaisey us chaand ko dekh rahe ho (usey dekhney main tum ko kisi qism ki bhi rukawat na hogi) ya ye farmaya ke tumhen iske deedaar mein matlab shuba na hoga isliye agar tum se suraj ke tuloo aur ghurub se pahley (fajr aur asr) ki namazon ke padhney mein kotahi na ho sakey to aisa zaroor karo. (kyonke un hi ke Tufail deedaar ilahi naseeb hoga ya un hi waqton mein ye dekhna naseeb hoga) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmai (وسبح بحمد ربك قبل طلوع الشمس وقبل غروبها) '' to apne rab ke hamd ki tasbeeh padh suraj ke nikalney aur uske ghurub honey se pahley .'' imam abu-Adbullah Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke ibne-Shahab ne Ismail ke waaste se jo Qais se b-waaste Jarir ( rawi hain) ye zyadti naql ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum apne rab ko saaf dekhogey''.
574,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne thandey waqt ki 2 namazein ( waqt par) padhein ( fajr aur Asr ( to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. ibne- -Rijaa ne kaha ke ham se Hammam ne abu-Jamra se bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar bin-Abdullaah-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein us hadis ki khabar di. ham se Ishaq ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Hibban ne, unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Hammam ne bayan kya, kaha ham se abu-Jamra ne bayan kya Abu-Bakar bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, pehli hadis ki tarah ."
575,"un logon ne (eik martaba ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sehrii khaai, phir Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey. maine malum kya ke un donon ke darmyan kis qadr fasla raha hoga. farmaya ke jitna pachaas ya sath aayat padhney mein sirf hota hai itna fasla tha."
576,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne sehrii khaai, phir jab wo sehrii kha kar farigh huey to Namaz ke liye uthey aur Namaz padhi. ham ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke aap ki sehrii se faraghat aur Namaz ki shuruaat mein kitna fasla tha? unhon-ne farmaya ke itna ke aik shakhs pachaas aayatein padh sakey."
577,"main apne ghar sehrii khaataa, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath namaze-Fajr paaney ke liye mujhey jaldi karni padtii thi."
578,musalman auratein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath namaaze-fajr padhney chaadaron mein lipat kar aati thin. phir Namaz se farigh ho kar jab apne gharon ko wapas hotiin to unhein andherey ki wjah se koi shakhs pehchan nahi sakta tha.
579,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne fajr ki aik rakaat ( jamat ke saath) suraj nikalney se pahley pa li usne fajr ki Namaz (baa-jamaa't ka sawaab) pa liya aur jisne Asr ki aik rakaat (jama'at ke saath) suraj doobney se pahley pa li, usne Asr ki Namaz (baa-jamaa't ka sawaab) pa liya."
580,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne aik rakaat Namaz (baa-jamaa't) pa li usne Namaz (baa-jamaa't ka sawaab) pa liya.
581,"mere samney chand moa'tabar hazraat ne gawahi di, jin mein sabse zyada moa'tabar mere nazdeek umr (Raziallahu anhu) they, ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fajr ki Namaz ke baad suraj buland honey tak aur Asr ki Namaz ke baad suraj doobney tak Namaz padhney se mana farmaya, ham se Musaddad ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se ke maine abul-Aaliyaa se suna, wo Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they ke unhon-ne farmaya ke mujh se chand logon ne ye hadis bayan ki. (jo pahley zikr huii)."
582,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Namaz padhney ke liye suraj ke tuloo aur ghurub honey ke intizar mein na baithey raho.
583,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab suraj ka uper ka kinara tuloo honey lagey to Namaz na padho yahan tak ke wo buland ho jaey. aur jab suraj doobney lagey us waqt bhi Namaz na padho, yahan tak ke ghurub ho jaey. us hadis ko Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ke sath Abda bin Sulaiman ne bhi riwayat kya hai."
584,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 tarah ki khareed w farokht aur 2 tarah ke libaas aur 2 waqton ki namazon se mana farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaze-Fajr ke baad suraj nikalney tak aur namaze-Asr ke baad ghurub honey tak Namaz padhney se mana farmaya (aur kapdon mein) ishtimaale-Sammaa yani aik kapda apne uper is tarah lapet lena ke sharmgah khul jaey. aur) احتباء ( yani aik kapdey mein gote mar kar baithney se mana farmaya, (aur khareed w farokht mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne munaabiza aur mulaamisa (phainkar aur chhookar Sauda karne) se mana farmaya,"
585,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, koi tum mein se intizar mein na betha rahe ke suraj tuloo hotey hi Namaz ke liye khada ho jaey, isi tarah suraj ke doobney ke intizar mein bhi na rehna chahiye"
586,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke fajr ki Namaz ke baad koi Namaz suraj ke buland honey tak na padhi jaey, isi tarah Asr ki Namaz ke baad suraj doobney tak koi Namaz na padhi jaey."
587,unhon-ne farmaya ke tum log to aik aisi Namaz padhtey ho ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein rahe lekin ham ne kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo Namaz padhtey nahi dekha. balke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to us se mana farmaya tha. Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki murad Asr ke baad 2 rakaton se thi ( jisey aap ke zamane mein kuchh log padhtey they).
588,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 waqt Namaz padhney se mana farmaya, namaze-Fajr ke baad suraj nikalney tak aur namaze-Asr ke baad suraj ghurub honey tak."
589,"jis tarah maine apne sathiyon ko Namaz padhtey dekha, mein bhi isi tarah Namaz padhta hon, kisi ko roktaa nahi. din aur raat ke jis hisse mein ji chahey Namaz padh sakta hai, albatta suraj ke tuloo aur ghurub ke waqt Namaz na padha karo."
590,"Allah ki qism ! jisne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne yahan bula liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaat ko kabhi tark nahi farmaya, yahan tak ke Aap (sl), Allah paak se ja miley aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wafat se pahley Namaz padhney mein badi dushwari pesh aati thi. phir aksar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar Namaz ada farmaya kartey they. agarche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein poori pabandi ke sath padhtey they lekin us khof se ke kahin (Sahaaba bhi padhney lagein aur us tarah) ummat ko bojh lage, unhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein nahi padhtey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni ummat ka halka rakhna pasand tha."
591,mere bhaanjey! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaat mere yahan kabhi tark nahi kin.
592,"aap ne farmaya ke 2 rakaton ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi tark nahi farmaya, posheeda ho ya aam logon ke saamney, subah ki Namaz se pahley 2 rakaat aur Asr ki Namaz ke baad 2 rak'aat."
593,unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke us kehney par gawahi di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bhi mere ghar mein Asr ke baad tashrif laey to 2 rakaat zaroor padhtey.
594,"ham abr ke din aik martaba Barida bin Hasib (Raziallahu anhu) sahabi ke sath they, unhon-ne farmaya ke Namaz sawerey padha karo. kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Asr ki Namaz chhodi iska amal akaarat ho gaya."
595,ham (khaibar se lot kar) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath raat main safar kar rahe they. kisi ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! aap ab padao daal detey to behtar hota. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey dar hai ke kahin Namaz ke waqt bhi tum sotey na reh jao. is par Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke main aap sab logon ko jaga doonga. chunanche sab log let gaey aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi apni peeth kajaawe se laga li aur unki bhi aankh lag gaee aur jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to suraj ke uper ka hissa nikal chuka tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Bilaal! tu ney kya kaha tha. wo boley aaj jaisi neend mujhey kabhi nahi aai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala tumhari ruhon ko jab chahta hai qabz kar leta hai aur jis waqt chahta hai wapas kar deta hai. aey Bilaal! uth aur azan de. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur jab suraj buland ho kar roshan ho gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur Namaz padhai.
596,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par (eik martaba) suraj ghurub honey ke baad aaey aur wo kuffaare-Quraish ko bura bhala keh rahe they. aur aap ne kaha ke aey Allah ke rasool! suraj ghurub ho gaya, aur namaze-Asr padhna mere liye mumkin na ho saka. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Namaz maine bhi nahi padhi. phir ham wadi Bathaan mein gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan Namaz ke liye wuzu kya, ham ne bhi wuzu banaya. us waqt suraj doob chuka tha. pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr padhai iske baad maghrib ki Namaz padhi."
597,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar koi Namaz padhna bhool jaey to jab bhi yad aa jaey usko padh ley. us qaza ke siwa aur koi kaffara uski wjah se nahi hota aur (Allah taala ne farmaya ke) Namaz mere yad aaney par qaaim kar. Musa ne kaha ke ham se Hammam ne hadis bayan ki ke maine Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo yun padhtey they Namaz padh meri yad ke liye. hibbaan-bin-Hilaal ne kaha, ham se Hammam ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Qatada ne, kaha ham se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, phir aisi hi hadis bayan ki."
598,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par (eik din) kuffaar ko bura bhala kehney lagey. farmaya ke suraj ghurub ho gaya, lekin main ( ladai ki wjah se) namaze-Asr na padh saka. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ham wadi Bathaan ki taraf gaey aur (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ki Namaz ( ghurub shams ke baad padhi iske baad maghrib padhi."
599,main apne bap Sulaamaa ke sath abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. unse mere walid sahib ne puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farz namazein kis tarah (yani kin kun oqaat mein) padhtey they. ham se iske barey mein bayan farmaiye . unhon-ne farmaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Zuhar) jisey tum صلوٰۃ اولیٰ kehtey ho suraj dhaltey hi padhtey they. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Asr padhney ke baad koi bhi shakhs apne ghar wapas hota aur wo bhi Madina ke sabse aakhiri kinare par to suraj abhi saaf aur roshan hota. maghrib ke barey mein aap ne jo kuchh bataya mujhey yad nahi raha aur farmaya ke isha mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) derii ko pasand farmatey they. us se pahley soney ko aur uske baad baat karne ko pasand nahi kartey they. subah ki Namaz se jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farigh hotey to ham apne qareeb baithey huey doosrey shakhs ko pehchan letey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr mein 60-100 tak aayatein padhtey they.
600,"aik din Hasan Basri (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne badi der ki. aur ham aap ka intizar kartey rahe. jab unke uthney ka waqt qareeb ho gaya to aap aaey aur) bataur ma'zirat ( farmaya ke mere un padausiyon ne mujhey bula liya tha (is liye der ho gai) phir batlaya ke Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha ke ham aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intizar kartey rahe. taqriban aadhi raat ho gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaey, phir hamein Namaz padhai. iske baad khutba diya. to aap ne farmaya ke dusron ne Namaz padh li aur so gaey. lekin tum log jab tak Namaz ke intizar mein rahe ho maano Namaz hi ki haalat mein rahe ho. imam Hasan Basri (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne farmaya ke agar log kisi khair ke intizar mein baithey rahen to wo bhi khair ki haalat hi mein hain. Qurra-bin-Khalid ne kaha ke Hasan ka ye qaul bhi Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ka hai jo unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki hai."
601,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz padhi apni zindagi ke aakhiri zamaney mein. salam pherney ke baad aap khadey huey aur farmaya ke us raat ke mutaalliq tumhen kuchh malum hai? aaj us poori zameen par jitney insan zinda hain. 100 saal baad unmein se koi bhi baqi nahi rahega. logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka kalam samajhney mein ghalati ki aur mukhtalif baatein karne lagey. (abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye samjha ke 100 baras baad qiyamat aaeygii) halanke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka maqsad sirf ye tha ke jo log aaj (is guftgu ke waqt) zameen par baste hain. unmein se koi bhi aaj se eik sadii ba'd baqi nahi rahega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka matlab ye tha ke 100 baras mein ye zamana guzar jaeyga
602,"ashabe-Suffa naadaar miskeen log they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske ghar mein 2 aadmiyon ka khana ho to wo teesrey ( ashabe-Suffa mein se kisi) ko apne sath leta jaey. aur jiske haan char aadmiyon ka khana hai to wo paanchwein ya chhatey aadmi ko saaybaan walon mein se apne sath ley jaey. to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) teen aadmi apne sath laey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) das aadmiyon ko apne sath ley gaey. Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ghar ke afraad mein us waqt baap, maan aur main tha. abu-Usman rawi ka bayan hai ke mujhey yad nahi ke Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-bakar ne ye kaha ya nahi ke meri biwi aur aik khaadim jo mere aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) donon ke ghar ke liye tha ye bhi they. khair Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan thahar gaey. (aur ghaaliban khana bhi wahin khaayaa. sura ye hui ke) Namaz isha tak wahin rahe. phir (masjid se) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hujra Mubarak mein aaey aur wahin thahrey rahe yahan tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi khana kha liya aur raat ka aik hissey guzar janey ke baad jab Allah Taala ne chaha to aap ghar tashrif laey to unki biwi (umme-Roomaan) ne kaha ke kya baat pesh aai ke mehmaanon ki khabar bhi aap ne na li, ya ye ke mehmaan ki khabar na li. aap ne poochha, kya tum ne abhi unhein raat ka khana nahi khilaaya. umme-Roomaan ne kaha ke main kya karun aap ke aaney tak unhon-ne khaney se inkar kya. khaney ke liye unse kaha gaya tha lekin wo na maaney. Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main dar kar chhup gaya Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne pukara aey ghunsar! (yani w paajii) aap ne bura bhala kaha aur kosney diye. farmaya ke khaao tumhen Mubarak na ho ! Allah ki qism ! main us khaney ko kabhi nahi khaaunga. (aakhir mehmaanon ko khana khilaaya gaya) (Abdur-Rehmaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) Allah gawah hai ke ham idhar aik luqma letey they aur nichey se pahley se bhi zyada khana ho jata tha. bayan kya ke sab logon ka pet bhar gaya aur khana pahley se bhi zyada bach gaya Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha to khana pahley hi itna ya usse bhi zyada tha. apni biwi se boley. banu-Faraas ki bahan! ye kya baat hai? unhon-ne kaha ke meri aankh ki thandak ki qasam! ye to pahley se teen guna hai. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi wo khana khaya aur kaha ke mera qism khana aik shaitaanii waswasa tha. phir aik luqma usmein se khaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Baqiiya khana le gaey aur aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey. wo subah tak aap ke paas rakha raha. Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke ham musalmanon ka aik doosrey qabeeley ke logon se muaahida tha aur muaahide ki muddat poori ho chuki thi. (is qabila ka wafad muaahide se mutaalliq baat cheet karne Madina mein aaya hua tha) ham ne unmein se baara aadmi juda kiye aur har aik ke sath kitney aadmi they Allah ko hi malum hai un sab ne unmein se khaayaa. Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuchh aisa hi kaha."
